ðŸ”§ 1. Convert with libx264 (CPU encoder)
ffmpeg -i input.mp4 \
  -c:v libx264 -preset veryfast -b:v 2000k \
  -c:a aac -b:a 128k \
  output-libx264.mp4


2. Convert with h264_qsv (Intel Quick Sync) Hardware accelerated:
ffmpeg -hwaccel qsv -i input.mp4 \
  -c:v h264_qsv -preset veryfast -b:v 2000k \
  -c:a aac -b:a 128k \
  output-qsv.mp4